I don't have a very good GPU so many of these settings are compromises. Things that can improve results:

* Using a different sampler than uniPC
* Using regular KSamplers instead of Tiled.
* Using 256px jumps instead of 128px.
* Different upscale models, check out https://upscale.wiki/wiki/Model_Database#Realistic_Photos
* Careful management of positive and negative prompts
* different model
* Lora and embeddings for landscapes or detail
